law.text:
Actions must be brought in the county in which the subject of the action, or some part thereof, is situated:
For the recovery of real property, or of an estate or interest therein;
For the partition of real property except as is provided in KRS 452.420;
For the sale of real property under a mortgage, lien, or other encumbrance or charge, except for debts of a decedent;
For an injury to real property.
